24/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/normani">诺曼尼</a>谈到了她期待已久的首张专辑《多巴胺》，称它将代表她“到达这一刻所经历的一切”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/noughties-pop-references-normanis-incredible-motivation-video-2539007">Normani 令人难以置信的“Motivation”视频中所有 00 年代流行音乐的点头</a></li></ul><p>本周早些时候（2 月 22 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/normani-announces-debut-solo-album-3590974">这位亚特兰大歌手公布了她首张个人全长唱片的封面艺术和名称</a>。这一消息是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/normani-new-music-on-the-way-album-singles-sundance-3574016">在一月份她调侃这张唱片后宣布的，称这是“实际上是她创作过的最好的音乐”。</a>在其他帖子中，她确认该专辑将于今年某个时候发行，但没有透露具体的发行日期。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.whowhatwear.com/fashion/celebrity/cover-features/normani-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Who What Wear</em></a>的新封面故事中，据说 Normani 即将发行的唱片将与她之前发行的嘻哈和 R&amp;B 倾向的流行音乐进行微妙的转变。这位 27 岁的歌手将这张专辑的声音描述为“[她的]进化的代表”。</p><p> “对我来说，这张即将发行的专辑不仅仅是音乐的问世，”她说。 “这感觉就像是我为了这一刻所经历的一切的代表。这张专辑给人一种解放的感觉，就像一个自由的季节。不仅仅是因为这张唱片终于面世了，还因为这是对一切的庆祝。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">等待是值得的。经过多年的期待， <a href="https://twitter.com/Normani?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Normani</a>以自己的方式重新回到聚光灯下。刚刚宣布了她的首张专辑《多巴胺》，她说这“感觉就像解放，就像一个自由的季节。不仅仅是因为唱片终于来了…… <a href="https://t.co/UFOipAy2rm">pic.twitter.com/UFOipAy2rm</a></p><p> — 谁穿什么 (@WhoWhatWear) <a href="https://twitter.com/WhoWhatWear/status/1760692167176233430?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 2 月 22 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>诺曼尼还透露，在发现父母都患有癌症后，她就不再听音乐了。</p><p> “我想做的就是陪伴他们，”她说。 “老实说，音乐帮助他们度过了癌症治疗。我记得我妈妈在接受化疗时，我和她通过 FaceTime 通话，她问我：‘今天工作室怎么样？音乐来得怎么样？”</p><p>她补充道：“虽然对我来说，不能像我想的那样和他们在一起很困难，但最终，坚持下去让我的父母感觉过去几年的情况变得轻松了一些。” </p><figure id="attachment_3592111" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3592111" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3592111" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-and-parents-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="（从左到右）安德里亚·汉密尔顿、诺曼尼和德里克·汉密尔顿在圣丹斯电影节综艺和金球奖派对上。图片来源：John Salangsang/Variety via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-and-parents-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-and-parents-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-and-parents-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-and-parents-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-and-parents-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-and-parents-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3592111" class="wp-caption-text"> （从左到右）安德里亚·汉密尔顿、诺曼尼和德里克·汉密尔顿在圣丹斯电影节综艺和金球奖派对上。图片来源：John Salangsang/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这位歌手作为女子组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fifth-harmony">Fifth Harmony</a>的一员而声名鹊起，该组合是在<em><a href="/tag/x-factor">The X Factor</a> US</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simon-cowell">Simon Cowell</a>的帮助下组建的。尽管没有赢得比赛节目，该乐队仍然取得了巨大的成功——发行了五张白金单曲和三张进入 Billboard 200 前五名的专辑，然后在 2017 年无限期停播。</p><p>诺曼尼告诉<em>Who What Wear，</em>第五和谐乐队解散后，她“需要时间、经验和空间”，这样她才能“成为[她]需要成为的自己。”</p><p> 《Dopamine》将于今年晚些时候通过 RCA Records 发行。<a href="https://www.wheresthedamnalbum.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处预先保存相册。</a> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3nvr2EPLGI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.6